# AVRCP spec PDFs are referenced by docs/AVRCP13-COMPLIANCE-PLAN.md §0 but
# not redistributable (Bluetooth SIG copyright). Place locally for citation
# verification; do not commit. Expected files (download from
# https://www.bluetooth.com/specifications/specs/a-v-remote-control-profile-1-3/):
#   AVRCP_SPEC_V13.pdf      — base spec (V13, 16 April 2007, 93 p.)
#   ESR07_ESR_V10.pdf       — Errata Service Release 07 (2013-12-03, 41 p.)
#   AVRCP.ICS.p17.pdf       — Implementation Conformance Statement (2024-07-01, 25 p.)
#   AVRCP.IXIT.1.6.0.pdf    — IXIT proforma (2014-09-18, 12 p.)
docs/spec/
